1. *Praviš* da ćeš da se vratiš kući? (Are you saying you will go back home?)

2. On *pravi* da je najbolji u igri. (He claims to be the best at the game.)

3. Oni *prave* planove za budućnost. (They are making plans for the future.)

4. Ja *pravim* ukusne obroke svakog dana. (I'm cooking delicious meals every day.)

5. *Praviš* li ti sam svoje čizme? (Are you making your own shoes?)

6. Oni *prave* razliku između dobrog i lošeg. (They are making a distinction between good and bad.)